CatDescriptText: Photo of the Monongahela River and Pittsburgh's South Side seen from Duquesne Heights.  In the foreground is the Smithfield Street Bridge and the Pittsburgh & Lake Erie Railroad Terminal, current site of Station Square.  Bridges in the distance are the Panhandle, Liberty, and Tenth Street bridges.
TitMainTitle: South side of Pittsburgh with Station Square and Smithfield Street bridge in foreground, along Monongahela River
